---------------------------------------------------------------------
Replicate time series regression functions for Matlab

Wolfram Liebermeister (2015)
---------------------------------------------------------------------


INSTALLATION

  1. Unpack the files

  2. Include the path to the matlab directory 'replicate_regression' into your Matlab path

  3. For a demo on a single replicate regression, run 'demo_replicate_regression'

  4. To see the application to a small omics data set, 
     run omics_data_example.m in the subdirectory replicate_regression/demo/omics_data_example
     A data and options file is provided in the subdirectory


REQUIREMENTS

  The functions were developed and tested with matlab6.


STATE OF THE SOFTWARE.

  The functions are under development and provided 'as is'.
  If you would like to contribute extensions to the toolbox, please let me know.


DOCUMENTATION

  Documentation (in directory 'doc') has been built automatically with M2HMTL


